com.clarionmedia.infinitum.orm.sqlite.impl

Class SqliteResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clarionmedia.infinitum.orm.sqlite.impl.SqliteResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResultSet

    public class SqliteResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements ResultSet

    This implementation represents a ResultSet from a SQLite database query. It's essentially a wrapper for a Cursor, which is what is typically used to represent SQLite relations.

    Version:
    1.0 02/23/12
    Author:
    Tyler Treat
